		As the <b>{{animal}}</b> approached, it became clear that it only wanted to share some of their <b>{{dessert}}</b>. <b>{{username}}</b> and <b>{{friend}}</b> were generous, and each gave the <b>{{animal}}</b> some of their <b>{{dessert}}</b>. 
